6
00:00:29,920 --> 00:00:45,746
This act allows public bodies to continue holding meetings remotely through March 31, 2023 without a quorum of the public body physically present at a meeting location and to provide adequate alternative access to remote meetings.

7
00:00:46,146 --> 00:00:55,150
In accordance with this act, this meeting of the City of Medford Energy and Environment Committee is being conducted totally via remote participation using Zoom.

